Super excited to be exhibiting “Knot Quite FREE” and some of the other work I made during my four month @longmeadowartresidency with @katesferriprojects in the “DARK MATTER” group exhibition opening this Friday January 13th with an Artists Reception from 6-8pm at Kates-Ferri Projects located at 561 Grand Street, NYC.   
  
I’ll be there and I’m looking forward to seeing you all!   
  
